 his starring role at the opening ceremony, Nadal was back doing what he does best on the stage he knows so well as he and Alcaraz claimed a 7-6 (4) 6-4 first-round victory in the men's doubles.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.5700231438192e-19, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4173286883397626e-18, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The illustrious Spanish pair made a slow start to the second set but clawed their way back from 0-3 down.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9901460045849998, \"rank\": 0.004997573348742784, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the two-time Wimbledon champion's thumping return that earned his team the crucial break for 5-4, and Nadal comfortably served out the victory.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"score\": 0.8950979552263683, \"rank\": 0.11379366842178398, \"text\": \"Wimbledon\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2009_Wimbledon_Championships\"}, {\"begi