/Rafah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the end, seeing the Philippe Chatrier stadium full, playing with Rafa, my first Olympics...\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"score\": 0.9999998153894182, \"rank\": 1.8449371756348307e-07, \"text\": \"Rafa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a moment, I will say, that was difficult to deal with the nerves.\\\"\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it was also a dream moment that the 21-year-old will cherish forever.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"It was a dream come true, honestly.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I dreamed about playing my debut in the Olympic Games, but playing with Rafa, it was even more special.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"score\": 0.9999998153894182, \"rank\": 1.8449371756348307e-07, \"text\": \"Rafa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really happy about the level we played, I am really happy to give us the chance to keep going, to play another round.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think our level is good enough to believe and hopefully keep going.\\\"\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, 38, played with strapping on his right thigh and there were question marks over whether the 14-time French Open champion would contest his scheduled singles match against Marton Fucsovics today (Sunday).\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\